{"tid":2131261,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[港產片希望？] 入嚟支持下呢班香港新演員啦","createTime":"2020-07-29T17:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T10:14:01.000Z","uid":15213,"like":13,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"76019fa39a405bfe32e766e60e54e8381e7aae59","tid":2131261,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T17:32:19.000Z","msg":"【JET Feature】新世代演員特集(一) <br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">顧定軒 vs 黃定謙</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://jet.my-magazine.me/public/resources/original/f5e2c49d63db00c1ad38b35b8d9affb0d6af6da6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjet.my-magazine.me%2Fpublic%2Fresources%2Foriginal%2Ff5e2c49d63db00c1ad38b35b8d9affb0d6af6da6.jpg&h=f8028c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://jet.my-magazine.me/public/resources/original/0296d18f182411b2b383f0a9e0a38b2a690780d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjet.my-magazine.me%2Fpublic%2Fresources%2Foriginal%2F0296d18f182411b2b383f0a9e0a38b2a690780d9.jpg&h=9de73fae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過去二、三十年，香港男主角像劉德華到古天樂，都予人剛強、英雄、極具男兒氣概，但現時電影電視行業，卻似乎沒有太多英雄角色。<br />\n<br />\nZeno Koo 顧定軒 和 黃定謙 WTHimmy ， 前者給人柔弱甚至中性的感覺，在《翠絲》中也有令人深刻的演出，後者也在《淪落人》中哭個不停，到底二人戲裡戲外有何落差？柔弱和淚眼又能否成為新血路？<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/314CJCP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F314CJCP&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=9f4490ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/314CJCP</a><br />\n<br />\n睇片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/143853769019573/posts/4082042155200695/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F143853769019573%2Fposts%2F4082042155200695%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=f34d255a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/143853769019573/posts/4082042155200695/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"0c63bbc881aef417769bca14291eff5feebcdac8","tid":2131261,"uid":15213,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T17:35:24.000Z","msg":"【JET Feature】新世代演員特集(二)  <br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">盧鎮業 vs 陳健朗</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://jet.my-magazine.me/public/resources/original/cc922224f9b98a863f55b0e313761fcfd96d00bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjet.my-magazine.me%2Fpublic%2Fresources%2Foriginal%2Fcc922224f9b98a863f55b0e313761fcfd96d00bd.jpg&h=954cc187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://jet.my-magazine.me/public/resources/original/65314d3d53ed0a9c593c08b4c925235246586852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjet.my-magazine.me%2Fpublic%2Fresources%2Foriginal%2F65314d3d53ed0a9c593c08b4c925235246586852.jpg&h=2430613e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n導演和演員，兩個身份中一定要二擇其一嗎？ 盧鎮業(小野) 首個紀錄片作品為《那年春夏．之後》，去年憑《叔&middot;叔》獲金像獎最佳男配角提名，也開辦電影製作公司兔角影像，今年帶來懸疑片《落葉殺人事件》。<br />\n<br />\n而陳健朗首個演出作品為《那夜凌晨，我坐上了旺角開往大埔的紅Van》，今年在《歎息橋》中飾演年輕版林保怡，執導作品《手捲煙》則獲得第四屆「首部劇情電影計劃」資助。<br />\n<br />\n二人在兩個身份中同時遊走，只是節奏不一。演而優則導，聽起來美好，但在性質差距下，二人都作出各自的取捨。建立個人品牌和背負團隊之間，他們往往有著雙重的考量。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/39Kqgbn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39Kqgbn&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=edacae17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/39Kqgbn</a><br />\n<br />\n睇片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/143853769019573/posts/4086078744797036/?vh=e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F143853769019573%2Fposts%2F4086078744797036%2F%3Fvh%3De&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=44c9ed2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/143853769019573/posts/4086078744797036/?vh=e</a>"},{"pid":"0599009ebe018bba3d002d37e44ca9c3135083b1","tid":2131261,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T17:40:08.000Z","msg":"【JET Feature】新世代演員特集(三)  <br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">岑珈其 vs 凌文龍</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://jet.my-magazine.me/public/resources/original/30c47236c70f3c72cebede687a79285039278361.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjet.my-magazine.me%2Fpublic%2Fresources%2Foriginal%2F30c47236c70f3c72cebede687a79285039278361.jpg&h=ae92af92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://jet.my-magazine.me/public/resources/original/5e3c34facbfdb72c2939509ac45cbd2f983f96f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjet.my-magazine.me%2Fpublic%2Fresources%2Foriginal%2F5e3c34facbfdb72c2939509ac45cbd2f983f96f1.jpg&h=739ee4ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自稱骨格精奇，又長得一臉天真。外型會局限可塑性， 岑珈其 和 凌文龍 的童顏，在演出上亦有危有機。珈其剛過三十歲，去年在《教束》中仍在演中學生，比人家佔優的是可以多演幾年學生，但愈演愈怕觀眾尷尬。而四年前，凌文龍曾在劇團中飾演十六歲的中學生，吊詭的是角色擁有三十多歲的思想，跳出跳入極考功架。<br />\n<br />\n雖然並非一眼便覺得是男主角的外型，但二人未想過如何突出自己，因為行業現在己經夠難行。「<span class=\"red\">如果有人要演得很亮麗、演得很強，但當劇本因而被忽略，其實沒意思。演員愈自私，愈難產生好東西。</span> 」一人好，不如大家都好。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/32ZVf1E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32ZVf1E&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=84e8f959\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/32ZVf1E</a><br />\n睇片：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/143853769019573/posts/4090975130974064/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F143853769019573%2Fposts%2F4090975130974064%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=7acd7e9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/143853769019573/posts/4090975130974064/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紅字好認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d460949e371c35cfac1192f730b7fdd4bf9d15a1","tid":2131261,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:23:19.000Z","msg":"推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog